1. I launched a Jenkins Bitnami server, available in AWS Marketplace.
2. Docker and Node are manually installed on that server.
3. A AWS Role with premissions to ECS, ECR, API, ELB, CloudWatch was attached to this instance.
4. Following Jenkins plugins are installed additionally.
   - CloudBees AWS Credentials Plugin
   - Amazon ECR plugin
   - Docker plugin
5. Existing VPC, Subnets and Security Groups are used.